### Release notes

This release of the game has polished UX, bug fixes, performance update, game design tweaks and a refresh of the game models and animations. It is hosted on Starknet Sepolia testnet, one step closer to Starknet mainnet.

### Competition information

There are up to 205,000 $Lords available to be won across four separate competitions.  At time of publishing thats a prize fund worth over $11,000 USD. Please follow the rules to participate in the competitions.

#### General rules

No entrant may mint over 4 Realms in the season.  Doing so excludes a player from the competition.  You can capture and operate 5+ Realms, but you cannot mint more than 4 Realms.

For this Preseason on Sepolia the competition will be coordinated by the Eternum team. Their decision in all matters relating to the competitions is final, and they reserve the right to disqualify players on any grounds. In future on mainnet Eternum seasons will be immutable, with the smart contract code maintaining integrity of gameplay and distribution of prizes.

