#### Creator competition

*10 creators will split 50k $Lords (5k $Lords each).*

The challenge:  Tell the story of the Eternum preseason and bring the world of Eternum to life.

\
This is a creative competition that will be judged by 3 DAO contributors who's decision of the winner is binding.

What the judges will be looking for:

- quality of storytelling
- the number of people that see and interact with it
- how well received it is in the community,
- how it is received in other channels (like X, YouTube, other communities etc),
- platform variety (streaming, X, YouTube, TikTok, Instagram).
- quality of targeted auidence (a relevant audience of crypto natives who love gaming)

As a bonus, the first 5 creators that can prove they have authentically generated a million non-spam impressions of relevant storytelling content can claim an additional 10k $Lords bounty, each.  This is an award to recognise virality, not to encourage spamming. All materials for consideration are to be supplied within 72 hours of the season closing.

To enter: tell your stories, then drop links, screenshots and any key information in the Creator Challenge discord channel.

